---
/* import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import StarShape2 from "../../assets/shapes/StarShape2.svg";*/
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import assemblee from "../../assets/business/assemblee.jpeg";
import Section from "./Section.astro";
---

<Section id="home">
  <div
    class="w-screen pt-[2rem] lg:pt-[1rem] relative flex flex-col lg:grid lg:grid-flow-col lg:grid-col-4 lg:grid-rows-4 justify-end bg-white gap-4 lg:max-h-screen px-0 lg:px-5"
  >
    <div
      class="flex flex-col lg:p-4 lg:row-span-4 lg:col-span-1 lg:grid pb-0 lg:pb-4"
    >
      <div
        class="items-left text-center lg:text-left w-full flex flex-col justify-between h-full"
      >
        <div class="relative space-y-3 py-4 lg:py-10">
          <div class="flex flex-row align-top">
            <h1
              class="pl-4 font-bold text-3xl pt-1 lg:pt-0 lg:text-5xl lg:font-medium leading-none motion-preset-slide-right motion-duration-2000"
            >
              L’art, clé de la cohésion et de l’engagement des équipes.
            </h1>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="lg:shadow-2xl lg:bg-purple lg:text-white lg:rounded-xl lg:w-full lg:min-h-[12rem] p-4 lg:p-4 text-xl lg:font-light"
        >
          <h1 class="font-bold text-xl lg:text-2xl pb-3 lg:pb-6">
            Nos conférences
          </h1>
          <span class="text-base lg:text-lg">
            Chez Artesemys, nous fusionnons l'art et la culture pour inspirer
            les équipes et améliorer la collaboration. <br
              class="lg:block hidden"
            /> Découvrez comment nos conférences uniques peuvent élever la dynamique
            de votre environnement de travail.</span
          >
        </div>
        <div
          class="hidden lg:block pl-4 pb-16 text-lg font-light text-center lg:text-left"
        >
          <button
            onclick="window.location.href='#services'"
            class="bg-purple hover:bg-white hover:text-dark hover:border-purple hover:border text-white font-bold py-6 px-14 rounded-full transition duration-500"
          >
            Nos services
          </button>
          <button
            onclick="window.location.href='#contact'"
            class="group hover:bg-purple hover:text-white bg-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-400 text-gray-800 font-bold py-6 px-14 rounded-full inline-flex items-center transition duration-500"
          >
            <span>Contactez-nous</span>
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 ml-2 text-dark group-hover:text-white transition duration-500"
              width="800px"
              height="800px"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
              <path
                clip-rule="evenodd"
                d="M12.2929 4.29289C12.6834 3.90237 13.3166 3.90237 13.7071 4.29289L20.7071 11.2929C21.0976 11.6834 21.0976 12.3166 20.7071 12.7071L13.7071 19.7071C13.3166 20.0976 12.6834 20.0976 12.2929 19.7071C11.9024 19.3166 11.9024 18.6834 12.2929 18.2929L17.5858 13H4C3.44772 13 3 12.5523 3 12C3 11.4477 3.44772 11 4 11H17.5858L12.2929 5.70711C11.9024 5.31658 11.9024 4.68342 12.2929 4.29289Z"
                fill="currentColor"
                stroke="currentColor"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col lg:col-span-3 pb-8">
      <div class="row-span-2 pt-[2rem] lg:pt-4">
        <Image
          src={assemblee}
          alt={""}
          class="shadow-2xl lg:rounded-xl lg:w-full lg:max-h-[90vh]"
          loading={"eager"}
        />
        <p
          class="px-2 lg:px-0 pt-4 text-xs lg:text-sm text-bold bottom-0 text-slate-600"
        >
          Transformez vos équipes grâce à nos conférences théâtralisées. <br />A
          travers différents thèmes nous saurons répondre à vos problématiques
          et offrir un moment de cohésion à vos équipes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="lg:hidden pl-4 text-base font-light text-left inline-flex pb-12 items-center justify-center"
    >
      <button
        onclick="window.location.href='#services'"
        class="bg-purple text-xs text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full"
      >
        Nos services
      </button>
      <button
        onclick="window.location.href='#contact'"
        class="bg-gray-300 text-xs text-gray-800 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full inline-flex items-left"
      >
        <span>Contactez-nous</span>
        <svg
          class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 text-dark"
          width="800px"
          height="800px"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="currentColor"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          <path
            clip-rule="evenodd"
            d="M12.2929 4.29289C12.6834 3.90237 13.3166 3.90237 13.7071 4.29289L20.7071 11.2929C21.0976 11.6834 21.0976 12.3166 20.7071 12.7071L13.7071 19.7071C13.3166 20.0976 12.6834 20.0976 12.2929 19.7071C11.9024 19.3166 11.9024 18.6834 12.2929 18.2929L17.5858 13H4C3.44772 13 3 12.5523 3 12C3 11.4477 3.44772 11 4 11H17.5858L12.2929 5.70711C11.9024 5.31658 11.9024 4.68342 12.2929 4.29289Z"
            fill="currentColor"
            stroke="currentColor"></path>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
